Comment: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:45.73,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not ignoring her was the right decision... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, maybe I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her body is extremely...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absurdly light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct, you could say that Senjougahara has no such thing as mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cultural festival is coming up, but we're already seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And studying for entrance exams is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just make a list of what we can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let everyone vote for it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, seems pretty democratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always have this mean tone to your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda rebellious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanekawa Tsubasa. She's our class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's well disciplined and courteous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so serious that it's scary, and all the teachers love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call her the representative of class representatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For reference, what did you do for the past two years' cultural festivals?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A haunted house and a café.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as the vice class representative,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently discussing what we should do for the cultural festival with Hanekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's someone called Senjougahara in our class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was just wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's usually absent because she's sick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was wondering if she'd come to the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think "Senjougahara Hitagi" is a weird and interesting name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara is a place name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara-san's first name is Hitagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so weird about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall correctly, "Hitagi" is some civil engineering term.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know everything, I just happen to know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually showed interest in someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess guys like frail girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frail, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, does that count as a sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what kind of person is Senjougahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know her better than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you've been in the same class as her for three years in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's a perfect honor student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has good grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've only been in the same class as her for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know her that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention Golden Week was during that month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Week, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Golden Week?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't talk much and it doesn't seem like she has any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's because she's always sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During middle school, she was a lot livelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During middle school? You went to the same middle school as her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara-san was extremely beautiful and great at sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the star of the track team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I heard a lot of things about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I heard she's a nice person who's very sociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her father is a big shot in a foreign corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she lives in a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, she doesn't show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superwoman much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't say this, but....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's much prettier now than she was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her existence is so delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her existence is so delicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino asked me to go to his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino-san? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm kinda helping him with his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanekawa, can I leave the rest to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you promise you'll make up for it, then sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it'd be bad to keep Oshino-san waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say hi to him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you and Hanekawa-san talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you can move if you want, but it'd be very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curiosity is like a cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It likes to stumble upon secrets that're supposed to stay hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty damn annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your right cheek feeling lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a banana peel to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... weightless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I say that, but I'm not actually weightless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my height and build, I should be around 45 kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my actual weight is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5 kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened before I entered this high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met a crab and it took away my weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right if you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just telling you because it'll be troublesome if you keep on sniffing around like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Araragi Koyomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what should I do in order to keep you quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do in order to make you swear you won't leak a word even if your mouth gets ripped open?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, all I want is your silence and apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like to promise me that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then nod twice, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All other actions including not responding will be taken as a no,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I will immediately go on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you didn't scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spare you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore me from tomorrow on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing, so I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanekawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:10:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be at Oshino-san's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanekawa, do you like bananas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, it's not that I dislike them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, they're very nutritious. But if I were to choose between liking and disliking them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd lean more towards liking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you like them, don't eat them at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay, you can eat them. But if you throw the peel on the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Araragi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run in the corridors!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I should really say I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd show resistance so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not go to war!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I might be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on. What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keeping your mouth shut and ignoring me is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kindness can sometimes translate to hostility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino... Oshino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Oshino Meme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Thanks to him, I transformed back into a human from a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,But it seems like there are a few side effects from immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Oshino Meme?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,His name sounds pretty moe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting your hopes up is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's some thirty year old guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was a moe character when he was small, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at someone 3D like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do you even understand what "moe" and "character" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those terms are basic knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess my character is what people call "tsundere", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your character is what people call "tsundra".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ass hurts. It's all numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my skirt is wrinkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make excuses or I'll cut it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut what off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's your backpack?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not holding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All my textbooks are in my locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's no point in having a backpack when I keep all of my school supplies on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't keep both of my hands free,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to fight freely if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hang on to your school supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look after it, so hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino might be a weird guy, but I consider him to be my savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let some dangerous person meet with my savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so let me look after your school supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You waited until we got here to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set me up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then. Please look after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm letting my guard down for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have 5000 grunts. If I were to go for a minute without contacting them, they would go and attack your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be fine, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean a minute's enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm some boxer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your two younger sisters are still in middle school, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't think I'll thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be the one thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to make the injury too obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I purposely stapled the inside instead of the outside of your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like saying, "The wound would stand out on his face, so I'll hit his stomach."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just convenient for the assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever, it seems like I was just wasting effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt if I say being immortal is convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not immortal anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that my wounds heal faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apart from that, I'm perfectly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun, I'm warning you one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not be able to tell with my clothes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but surprisingly enough, my body isn't worth the jail time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're either too insecure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or your persecution complex has gotten way out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, there are things you should say and there are things you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's aware?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:17:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back on topic, I can't believe that this Oshino guy lives in a building that looks like it's about to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's a pretty weird guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's an expert in cases like yours and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought a different girl again along with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it. Don't write me off as some low class character.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you too, I'm Senjougahara Hitagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a classmate of Araragi-kun's and he told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino, two years ago, this chick{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "this chick".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Se-n-jo-u-ga-ha-ra-sa-ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the way you pronounced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara-chan{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to blind me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one told you to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of equivalent exchange is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My harsh remarks are made by\Ntransmutating 40g of copper, 25g of zinc,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15g of nickel, 5g of hiding my\Nembarrassment along with 97kg of spite.{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that nearly all spite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I was lying about "hiding my embarrassment".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took out the most important ingredient!{trying to keep w/FMA theme}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of that. What is that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has neither shadow nor form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has neither name nor existence. That's what she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave her a name yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she helped me a lot during Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? She has a name now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Oshino Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A heart under the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name suits her, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let her use my surname.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I asked what exactly she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, she's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ruined vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leftovers of a beautiful demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say that, but it doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so she's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I heard you could save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can save yourself, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were five people who spat the exact same lines at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all scammers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the same as them, Oshino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well aren't you lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something nice happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, we can't get further if you don't tell me your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep it a secret, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me explain it briefly{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell him by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's folklore from the mountains of Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the location, its name varies from weighty crab to heavy stone crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even heavy stone god. That means crabs and gods are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why Kyushu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place itself doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as certain conditions are met, it'll appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, it doesn't have to be a crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are rumors of it being a rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also rumors of it being a beautiful woman. It's not Shinobu-chan though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like the patterns on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if this young lady met a crab,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's a crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it before, it might be a God rather than a crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heavy crab was derived from the heavy stone God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're a lucky one out of the unlucky bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:20:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gods are everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're everywhere, yet nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say it was both around you and not around you before you became like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like Zen dialog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shinto. Or perhaps it's Shugendou?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't become like this because of whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that your point of view changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My point of view? What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I can't stand you acting all victimized, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a selfish person, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans who meet heavy crabs are usually like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see it just because you want to,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's not a harmful God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not harmful?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just there and it won't appear if you don't wish for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't wanna delve so deep into your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to regain your weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were referred here by Araragi-kun, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:23:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukihi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the preview quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.82,0:23:58.69,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:23:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hit and beat" refers to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it refer to Karen-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this "&" stand for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question isn't hard, but it's hard to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, Hitagi Crab, Part 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show it to the people who answered correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're showing it to no one.
